      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "For the chemical structure processing, our package utilizes Tanimoto similarity, a commonly used and rigorously tested metric for physicochemical comparisons... It performs these comparisons using the 'fmcsBatch()' function from the R package fmcsR",
      "asbval:note": "Both Tanimoto and FMCS metrics are used for filtering and comparison.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1371-journal-pone-0306202",
