      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "After identifying perfect matches (i.e., those with high match factors and the same chemical names) the algorithm looks again through each sample for instances where the top 2 published m/z values for the tentative identity are the same as the query chemicals of interest.",
