      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "uafR also interacts with structural data [in SDF (Structure-Data format)] for all published compounds in the dataset. These data allow detailed summaries of the chemical constituents for each sample to be generated based on the user's chemical(s) of interest.",
