      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "For the chemical structure processing, our package utilizes Tanimoto similarity, a commonly used and rigorously tested metric for physicochemical comparisons. This information is generated using the 'read.SDFset()' function from another R package called ChemmineR [33]. This package is a dependency that is installed with uafR and is core to the cheminformatics methods deployed.",
