    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/mass-spectrometry-match-factor-filtering/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "A simple and effective approach is to subset the search chemicals by setting a minimal match factor on the raw output of Unknowns Analysis (or other GC -MS software). This can be done with R code described in the vignette published with the package.",
