      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The categorical data include whether the chemical is biologically derived [Natural Products Online database (LOTUS)], has flavor or smell [Flavor and Extract Manufacturers Association (FEMA)], has varied biological activities [Kyoto Encyclopedia of Genes and Genomes (KEGG)], medical subject headings (MeSH), or other information about their reactivity [Food and Drug Administration\u2014Structured Product Labeling (FDA/SPL) and Reactive Groups from PubChem].",
