      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "We have developed an R package, uafR, that automates a grueling retrieval process for gas -chromatography coupled mass spectrometry (GC -MS) data... After reading the data into R and loading the package, uafR can use published information to sort and precisely select portions of the data that the user may be interested in.",
      "asbval:note": "R is confirmed as the environment for uafR execution.",
